'''Gryseium Incorporated''' was a ranch founded by [[Huegu Eib]], a [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]], but later sold to [[Rigis Corazon]]. It was located in the clouds of [[Tyed Kant]], a planet in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]]. Corazon attempted to use Gryseium Incorporated to corner the food market on [[Demophon]], but failed due to a lack of a contract with the Demophonian government or the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. His daughter, [[Sabel Axis Corazon]], later took control over the company.

